				</div>
			
		
			
				<p class="lia-message-dates lia-message-post-date lia-component-post-date-last-edited" class="lia-message-dates lia-message-post-date">
					
		 <span class="DateTime lia-message-posted-on lia-component-common-widget-date" class="DateTime lia-message-posted-on">
    

	
		
		
		<span class="local-date">‎03-12-2015</span>
	
		
		<span class="local-time">03:18 PM</span>
	
	

	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
</span>
	
				</p>
			
		
			
				
						
		<div class="lia-message-body lia-component-body" id="messagebodydisplay_0_7" class="lia-message-body">
	
		<div class="lia-message-body-content">
			
                
                    <P><FONT size="3" face="times new roman,times">Chapter 17: At the Magma Tops Part 2</FONT></P><P>&nbsp;</P><P><FONT size="3" face="times new roman,times">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Barber looked at them sadly and then walked to them. The other left, but he was still looking at the guards, Barber and them. Shadow thought that he did not want to give the idea of having anything to do with the Nexus-Forcers. The three friends watched Barber talking to the two guards. They seemed to be angry. Then, one of them kicked him and Barber fell down with a grimace of pain. And before the three of them could react, the other aimed his rifle… and fired.</FONT></P><P><FONT size="3" face="times new roman,times">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Shadow kept looking emptily at the same spot, even when the guards turned their eyes on them and made for them. When Kate grabbed his arm and pulled him running, he didn’t really feel it. He had felt too much pain in his life, yet he still was surprised by the cruelty that there was in some parts of the Universe. Minifigures smashing… minifigures! For no reason! Had they not had enough with the Maelstrom? Shadow had just watched one of them being smashed just because he was talking them. Barber probably knew of the danger, yet he still tried to warn them. He couldn’t understand how there could be so much cruelty in one person.</FONT></P><P><FONT size="3" face="times new roman,times">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Shadow still did not react when the bullets started raining around them, when one hit him on the leg, when they passed over a bridge over a lava stream, when they jumped over little lava puddles and smaller streams, when they passed through a cave that besides lava, also had Maelstrom hints, when they got in an area with obvious infection by Maelstrom… He was passive to the world.</FONT></P>
                
            
			
				<div style="width:98%; max-height:100px; overflow:hidden;" class="UserSignature lia-message-signature">
	҈ Sίr Shαdow, the fίrςt plαyer of the V fς, the Ice Cream Eater of SoL Evil/Insane Genious İDFTBA! ҉<BR />Inventor of the ch<img class="emoticon emoticon-laughing" id="laughing" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/laughing.png" alt="Laughing" title="Laughing" />pters and the alien tongue smiley :: P <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" />! One post to rule them all! <img class="emoticon emoticon-whistling" id="whistling" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/whistling.png" alt="Whistling" title="Whistling" /><BR />Bewαre of the shαdows becαuse I might be there.
